{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10651f4ffe","title":"陈伯达江青给北京航空学院\"红旗\"的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e5c90b3fcf","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":26,"articleId":"10651f4ffe","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"吴德","id":"7f0393737e","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"282eb6cbd9","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"1967年3月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（1）》"}],"contents":[{"id":"a0c6e8ecfb","type":"title","text":"陈伯达江青给北京航空学院\"红旗\"的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78017cd6e7","type":"paragraph","text":"起草一个决定，不必开誓师大会，考虑准备北京市工农兵和革命师生代表会，组织市人民政府，不一定用市长这一形式，标语和传单暂不印，转告（其它组织）。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06a0ff6873","type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵都派代表参加。那一些可以接管，用什么形式，应经代表会研究。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"806ffeb031","type":"paragraph","text":"立即放吴德同志回去，监督其工作，代表会马上准备工农兵代表会，代表会不能交给这一派，也不能交给那一派。北京市学生多比例可多一些，可搞主任，轮流主持会议。接管问题，可在会上充分讨论。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7f4e902bd","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志传达主席一句话：凡是搞宗派主义，小团体主义，最后都搞不成的，把这个精神传给其它组织。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10651f4ffe","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}